title: CLOUD SYSTEMS IN SUPPLY CHAINS

Soliman Edition: 1st ed. 2015 edition Publication Date: January 14, 2014 Publisher: Palgrave Macmillan ISBN-10: 134967298X ISBN-13: 978-1349672981 Pages: 319 pages Format: pdf Size: 3.5M --- Cloud Systems in Supply Chains explores the risks that could face supply chain firms if their implementation of cloud systems is not carefully managed or if not appropriately selected and supported.
